<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 May 2022 02:46:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>ASUS TUF Gaming Capture Box FHD120     120fps FHD 遊戲機、電腦畫面錄片   </title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/26/asus-tuf-gaming-capture-box-fhd120/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=asus-tuf-gaming-capture-box-fhd120</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 26 May 2022 02:46:11 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[配件]]></category><category><![CDATA[影片擷取]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1101141</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>現時愈來愈多玩家會將自己遊戲過程直播到網上，或是錄影遊玩片段，以方便分享及製作攻略影片之用。而 ASUS 較早 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">現時愈來愈多玩家會將自己遊戲過程直播到網上，或是錄影遊玩片段，以方便分享及製作攻略影片之用。而 ASUS 較早前就推出了高階版本的 CU4K30，不過 4K 影片始終在剪接及儲存上要求都比 FHD 影片高得多，所以 ASUS 就推出了入門級的 FHD120。以更親民的價格推出市場，以吸引對 4K 擷取沒有要求的玩家選擇。</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;">USB 即插即用</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus05.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101146" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus05-694x530.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="530" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus05-694x530.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus05-768x587.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus05.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">ASUS 這款 FHD120 採用 USB 傳輸介面，支援 4K60、2K60、1080p120 影像輸入，同時亦支援 Pass Through 輸出。影片擷取部分最高可支援至 1080P 120fps 無壓縮錄制輸出，同時內置 3.5mm 輸入及輸出接口，支援 Windows PC、 PlayStation / Xbox / Nintendo Switch 等裝置的影片擷取能力。同時 Windows 部分支援 UVC 免安裝驅動功能，即插即用，令使用變得更簡單。</p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101147" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-900x900.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01-2048x2048.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus01.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a>▲金屬機身設計，配上 RGB 燈效。</p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101148" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-900x900.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02-2048x2048.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus02.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a>▲前方提供 3.5mm 音效輸入及輸出接口。</p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101149" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-900x900.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03-2048x2048.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus03.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a>▲包裝已經提供齊全的 USB 接線。</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;">零噪音散熱設計</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101150" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus04.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">可能讀者會奇怪，FHD120 機身好像比較大，但 ASUS 就用上金屬散熱底蓋設計，配合機身散熱口，做到零噪音運作方式，確保不會有任何風扇聲音，以免影響直播時的錄音。機身採用 RGB 設計，用家可以在運作時，直接以顏色得知運作狀態，出現問題又或是有錯誤設定，用家可以即時從燈號得知問題所在。</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;">直接支援 OBS Studio</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">和大部分影片擷取裝置一樣，ASUS TUF Gaming Capture Box FHD120 並未提供直播軟件，而是直接取得 OBS Studio 認證。用家只需要透過 USB 連接 FHD120 到電腦，就可以在 OBS 中以視訊擷取裝置選項加入 FHD120 到直播來源中，任何用家都可以簡單完成設定。設定部分沒有任何難度，只需要你的來源提供 FHD 120fps 規格，就可以直接以 FHD 120fps 設定擷取影像資料。</p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus06.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus06-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus06-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus06-768x443.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus06.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> ▲ASUS 亦有提供硬件控制軟件，可直接改變不同的音量控制，以便用家控制直播品質。</p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus07.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus07-694x400.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="400" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus07-694x400.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus07-768x443.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/asus07.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲機身燈除了狀態顯示模式外，亦可以在軟件中自由設定。</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;">至適合入門用家</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">可能有用家擔心電腦效能影響到遊玩時的體驗，所以 ASUS 亦為用家提供 Pass Through 功能，令影像可以在完全沒有影響下輸出到螢幕，完全避免任何影像延遲出現。而免驅動設計加上 FHD 120fps 擷取能力，已經足以應付家用機及中階 PC 平臺直播需要，整體來說最為適合入門用家使用。</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;">ASUS TUF Gaming Capture Box FHD120 影像擷取盒</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">售價︰HK$1,399</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">查詢：<a href="https://bit.ly/3FKeNbr">https://bit.ly/3FKeNbr</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
