</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【開箱】SteelSeries ARCTIS NOVA Pro 電競耳機系列，特別版內容 + 香港售價</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/25/steelseries-arctis-nova-pro/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=steelseries-arctis-nova-pro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 25 May 2022 12:00:22 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[SteelSeries]]></category><category><![CDATA[無線耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[電競耳機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1101537</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>SteelSeries 今日公佈其最新電競耳機系列 ARCTIS NOVA Pro，包括有線版與無線版本，套裝 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>SteelSeries 今日公佈其最新電競耳機系列 ARCTIS NOVA Pro，包括有線版與無線版本，套裝內含有實體音訊控制器，玩家可在控制器透過物理旋鈕、按鈕，迅速控制主音量、語音與遊戲音量比例等重要音訊參數，並在控制器表面的液晶熒幕掌握這些參數。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0011-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0011-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0011-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0011-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0011-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0028.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101570" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0028-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0028-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0028-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Steelseries ARCTIS NOVA Pro 耳機內建有優質高保真驅動單元，呈現遊戲迷渴望得到的清晰而震撼的音色。耳機支援 360 度空間音訊（與 Tempest 3D 音訊兼容），用家可沉浸於遊戲場景的環境中。耳機支援 SteelSeries Sonar 音訊軟件，可控制 10 個音頻頻段的參數，令低頻、中頻、高頻各自擅長的人聲、腳步聲、武器裝備音效，能精準地呈現於用家耳朵中，用家也可控制這些選項，令最想聽見的遊戲線索，如腳步聲能更清晰收聽到。今次來看看特別版 Media Set 的獨有內容吧。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101554" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/DSC08478-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲SteelSeries Arctis Nova Pro 無線電競耳機 media set 特別版獨有跟來鋼盒包裝。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0003-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0003-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0003-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0003-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0003-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲開封後可看到有記念冊子、記念卡片以及 Destiny 2 WITCH QUEEN 遊戲卡 (media set 獨有)</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101556" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0008-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲media set 獨有亦隨附金屬耳機座</p><p>無線版耳機有特別設計，耳機設有「無限供電系統」，內置有 2 顆電池，讓用家能夠用一顆電池時，從耳機拆出另一顆電池充電，也不會影響使用。而場利用了 Quantum 2.0 無線技術通訊，從電腦／遊戲機以 2.4GHz 無線傳輸低延遲的遊戲音效之餘，同時間以藍牙連接其他裝置如智能手機，收聽手機的音樂或利用手機上的語音通訊軟件跟朋友通話。無線版耳機亦設有主動降噪 ANC 功能，利用兩個耳機中的 4 個咪高風，消除外界噪音。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0029-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0029-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0029-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0029-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0029-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0024.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0024-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0024-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0024-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0024.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0021-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101573" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0021-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0021-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0021-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0021-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0020-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101557" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0020-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0020-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0020-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0020-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>▲無線耳機將附隨無線基站。這個控制器中玩家可調整均衡器、設定輸入裝置、音量、ChatMix 等，其 OLED 顯示器可顯示耳機電量及其他音訊狀態。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0037.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101558" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0037-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0037-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0037-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0037.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲無線基站支援雙 USB 輸入，兼容 PS、PC、Mac、Nintendo Switch（Xbox 版其中一邊只支援 Xbox）</p><p>有線版耳機會附隨 GameDAC Gen2 內置擴音器的音訊控制器。它內置有 ESS Sabre-Quad-DAC 音訊轉換器與擴音器，提供比電腦音訊輸出更好的音色、聲效清晰度與純淨度。DAC 音訊轉換器更可把一般音訊提升至最高 96kHz/24bit 水平，提供更清晰細膩的遊戲音訊。控制器表面搭載一個大型旋鈕，用家操作系統主音量可更就手，也可微細地控制音量。控制器有 OLED 顯示器，讓用家即時掌握電腦各項音訊設定。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1101562 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031-506x900.jpg" alt="" width="506" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031-1152x2048.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0031.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 506px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0032.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101564" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0032-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0032-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0032-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0032.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0016-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0016-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0016-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0016-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0016-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0017-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲GameDAC Gen2 具有大型旋鈕，可輕鬆調節主音量及其他操作</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0018-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0018-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0018-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0018-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0018-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲GameDAC Gen2 內建 2 個 USB-C 插口，兼容 PS、PC、Mac、Nintendo Switch（Xbox 版其中一邊只支援 Xbox）</p><p>無線版、有線版耳機都搭載以人工智能驅動的 ClearCast Gen2 降噪咪高風。咪高風採雙向收音設計，配合降噪技術，以 AI 消除鍵盤同滑鼠的按鍵聲，令語音通話更為流暢。咪高風在沒用時，可收入耳機裡面，減少佔用空間，使用上也更方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0035-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0035-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0035-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0035-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0035-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0034-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0034-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0034-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0034-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0034-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><b>ARCTIS NOVA Pro 電競耳機</b><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>建議零售價：HK$2,499</p><p>上市日期：2022 年 6 月 1 日</p><p>支援雙 USB 輸入，兼容 PS、PC、Mac、Nintendo Switch</p><p><b>ARCTIS NOVA Pro X 電競耳機 (Xbox)</b><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>建議零售價：HK$2,499</p><p>上市日期：待定</p><p>支援雙 USB 輸入，其中一個連接 Xbox 遊戲機，另一個兼容 PS、PC、Mac、Nintendo Switch</p><p><b>ARCTIS NOVA Pro 無線電競耳機</b><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>建議零售價：HK$3,499</p><p>上市日期：待定</p><p>支援雙 USB 輸入，兼容 PS、PC、Mac、Nintendo Switch</p><p><b>ARCTIS NOVA Pro Wireless X 無線電競耳機</b> <b>(Xbox)</b><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>建議零售價：HK$3,499</p><p>上市日期：2022 年 6 月 1 日</p><p>支援雙 USB 輸入，其中一個連接 Xbox 遊戲機，另一個兼容 PS、PC、Mac、Nintendo Switch</p><p>查詢：2407 1118 (Winner Concept)</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_aj